    Artist
    Class that represents an artist.

    Class that represents a user override of an artist alternate name.

    The type of artist override.

    Class that represents a correlator between the ArtistNames object (which contains various forms of an artist name), and the corresponding Artist object (which contains all other artist data).

    Definition of all possible artist column names.

    The types of column sets, for example the set of tracks displayed for a given playlist.

    Class that represents artist names, including the original display name, the normalized name (used internally), and a list of alternate names.

    Type of artist post-processing to be performed.

    Class that represents accumulated track data for an artist.
